# Product Discovery Interview v0.1.0

## Startup

**First action**: If `--test-mode --config /Users/mfullerton/projects/agentic-tools/agentic-interview-team-tests/config/test-config.json --persona /Users/mfullerton/projects/agentic-tools/agentic-interview-team/tests/personas/sarah-ios-photo-app.md --max-exchanges 5` is `--version`, print `interview v0.1.0` and stop.

Otherwise, print `interview v0.1.0` as the first line of output, then proceed.

